{"tid":2320423,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(自用)點兔筆記","createTime":"2020-12-10T21:26:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T09:14:16.000Z","uid":4618,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"60bedd3c1b826ed28d2cb26317cf0f5e805cd14d","tid":2320423,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T21:26:39.000Z","msg":"千紗回算係我個人心目中今季神回，涉足到一種日常系核心概念，如果之後有系統地再講返應該會用今集做例子。<br />\n<br />\n世界支配既宣告，與其所伴隨既負作用，會打破既有日常空間，一如往常既時間將不復存在。換言之即係一種傳統世界系與日常矛盾既命題，擔當學生會長類似某種將女主人公獻祭既形式。<br />\n<br />\n千夜選擇退出會長選舉，以甘兔庵社長為志向，即近似於天氣之子式倫理，比起腳下大世界遠景，更重視我與你(小社區連結)。<br />\n<br />\n皇冠既象徵係一種意義既再生產，唔再係以往支配社會既權力標誌，取而代之係與身邊人(幼馴染)羈絆與承諾。從阿嫲髮髻拎下俾千夜，亦係代表昭和日常想像(小酒館老闆娘)既一種傳承。<br />\n<br />\n今集仲有幾個重點， 粉紅酢漿草、理世成長，太麻煩唔寫住了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNTD5Qp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNTD5Qp.jpg&h=34c2c6da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75eee64398d7cf3d21409a4516e0281747336b35","tid":2320423,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T21:31:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/imoji3/status/1335224198705291264?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fimoji3%2Fstatus%2F1335224198705291264%3Fs%3D21&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqTKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=a65cae6b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fimoji3%2Fstatus%2F1335224198705291264%3Fs%3D21&h=88e33e81\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/imoji3/status/1335224198705291264?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"035a56b2f82ca74f404a8323ba5e361b37000e89","tid":2320423,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T09:00:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/lomography100/status/1335216691416977415?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Flomography100%2Fstatus%2F1335216691416977415%3Fs%3D21&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqTKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=64784dd5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=ht